public abstract class DoublePStableFactory
extends DoubleHashFunctionFactory
    Base class for hashing schemes based on P-Stable distributions. The hash functions are of the form h(x) = floor((ax + b) / w).
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
